# Raycasts #

The method scene.pickWithRay throws a ray in your scene. 


Predicate function : 

function predicate (mesh){

  return mesh === target;

}

It will return true if the target has been hitten.





Global to local space coordinates converting :

 function local(argMesh, argVec){

    var matrix = argMesh.getWorldMatrix();
    var vector = BABYLON.Vector3.TransformCoordinates(argVec, matrix);
    return vector;

}// local() 





